    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Killistar: A 2D/3D Remake of the Classic Arcade Game Sinistar</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An adrenaline-fueled shoot-'em-up where the player must race against time to prevent the deadly <strong>Killistar</strong> from being fully constructed.  Mine crystals from asteroids, using them to power up a high-energy weapon—the only weapon capable of stopping <strong>Killistar</strong>.   Balance combat, resource gathering, and weapon upgrades as you battle waves of enemies in this action-packed remake that blends classic arcade gameplay with modern 2D and 3D elements.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Killer Space Robot comes to destroy HUMANITY</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Years after the beings exiled off the planet Earth, he is reborn as <strong>Killistar</strong>.  A planet killing robot monster looking to take control of the universe.  You command the only hope for earth, equipped with a super weapon capable of destroying <strong>Killistar</strong>. </p>",
